data.description: Looking for a beautiful and quiet neighborhood in Grove City? Welcome home to 3155 Kingswood Drive. This adorable 4-bedroom, 2 full bath Bi-Level home is located in Kingswood Heights and won't last long! Walking distance from Windsor Park and less than a mile from Broadway. Hardwood floors throughout most of 1st floor, updated Kitchen with granite counter tops and SS appliances with eating space, to the right of kitchen there are 3 spacious bedrooms and 1 full bath. LL offers large primary suite, FB, and laundry. Entry from the garage on lower level opens to a bonus space for a mud room, office or extra storage. 2 tier deck and firepit with sliding door entry on both levels. Fenced in yard, New Roof 2023, HVAC, Water Heater, Sump Pump all new in 2020. Concrete Driveway poured May 202
